oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Free and Accepted Masons pinning
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of attorney Leighton Ewell (1875-1973) receiving his fifty year membership pin from Highland Post Free and Accepted Masons #214. David W. Shields, Jr. (1899-1980) of Tullahoma, Post Master of the Lodge, is pinning it on him.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
